
To build:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

Or for verbose and to run tests:

make VERBOSE=1 all test


On Mac OSX, you will need to build and install Boost with 32-bit support.
The following will build the libraries with 32 and 64-bit architecture.

/bjam address-model=32_64 architecture=x86 link=static install

Libraries and tools used:

Cuda
http://developer.nvidia.com/object/gpucomputing.html
http://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/3_0/toolkit/docs/online/index.html

